1D\u003C/em\u003E said Secretary Read. \u003Cem\u003E\u201CMy goal is to build an audit team laser focused on improving the performance of state government. Steve has the background, skills, and experience to help us achieve that goal. This work is about delivering better results for the people of Oregon, not chasing headlines or advancing political agendas.\u201D\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n    \u003Cbr\u003E\n    Bergmann is currently the Business Services Director for the Secretary of State\u2019s office. Previously, he led audits at the Oregon Department of Fish and Wildlife and the Oregon Department of Revenue. Before his time with the State of Oregon, he worked for several accounting firms serving clients in the banking, nonprofit, and government sectors.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n    \u003Cbr\u003E\n    \u003Cem\u003E\u201CI appreciate the Secretary\u2019s confidence and look forward to restoring faith, stability, and reliability into the audits division,\u201D\u003C/em\u003E said Bergmann. \u003Cem\u003E\u201CThe Secretary has asked me to focus on establishing a transparent and data-backed risk assessment methodology, maximizing the capacity of all the audit team\u2019s resources, and producing audits that help agencies improve their performance. I cannot wait to get started.\u201D\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n    \u003Cbr\u003E\n    Bergmann will begin serving in his new role on January 13, 2025.\n\u003C/p\u003E","footer_content":"","category_tags":"","date_entered":"1/9/2025","entered_by":"","date_last_modified":"1/9/2025","last_modified_by":"Griffin Walker","category_tag1":"Improving Government","id":"272796145221523","postSlug":"secretary-of-state-tobias-read-appoints-steve-bergmann-as-director-of-audits-division"},{"agency":"Secretary of State","agencyAlias":"SOS","headline":"Secretary of State Tobias Read Sworn In to Office","subheadline":"","publish_date":"1/7/2025 9:02:27 AM","publish_year":"2025","city":"Sa